{
  "stem": "10406.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 34.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I saw this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, we saw most of the Russian personnel basically getting out of town as fast as they could.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there was a problem being that we were so close to the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the German armies actually by then probably, sort of, bypassed our town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were probably ahead on the sides, so there was, like, a small window of opportunity to get out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you could get out still because we were not far from the city [POLISH], which was a railroad sort of junction, and if you got there, you were able to get on a train and still make it to Russia.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew-- we knew that war broke out, that the Germans attacked-- attacked Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, we did not know the significance of what was going to happen to Jews, although by then, we should have known because by 1941, the Germans already did a job on the Polish Jews that was under their occupation.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They already had a ghetto, I believe, in Lublin at that point, and they were already persecuting and killing Jews in a lesser way in the rest of Poland and Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then-- it took a few days, and then suddenly, the Germans were marching into our town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember being on that street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were coming in on the main street that goes between [POLISH] and [POLISH] and [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw a little table, and the rabbi-- the rabbi and another man sitting at the table with bread and salt, which was a traditional way of welcoming, like, an invading army.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans were marching in the middle of the street, the main army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the officers broke rank and ran over to that little table and kicked it over, and told the rabbi and the other man to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know what the significance, what-- what it meant, but it was sort of a scary and unfriendly act.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ran-- I ran away from there, you know, when I saw that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And and that army marched-- most of it marched past town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them marched-- there was a big-- there was a monastery that also had, like, a high school before the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was mainly, like, Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the Russians came in, they made their headquarters there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It had a lot of ground area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now the Germans took over the Russian headquarters and they set up in the same place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of these soldiers marched there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the soldiers disappeared, basically, from the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a very short period of time, a new group moved into town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came in on motorcycles with machine guns and trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not many trucks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we found out that those were what they call the Einsatzgruppen, that were SS-- SS groups that are specifically trained to follow the main army right behind the main army and kill as many civilians as they wanted to, like, in a first sweep.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And although they didn't specify Jews at that point, they-- their objective was political prisoners and political people, anybody accused of being a communist, a communist sympathizer, and Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We still didn't-- maybe some of the adults, maybe, had a different feeling, but basically, there was some fear, but I don't think we knew exactly what we were fearing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that point we still went out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe not play per se, we were still out on the street because the atmosphere was already tense, and they did have German, you know, policing the streets, even though you didn't have the main army body there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened is as soon as the SS moved in, they issued an order that all Jewish males from 16 to 60 should report to the center of town in order to change passports.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was part-- that's when they--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's the same group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Einsatzgruppen are basically the SS that came in with-- with that purpose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whoever doesn't report would be shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the next morning, most-- many of the people reported.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for some reason again, I was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was too young yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't old enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to be, you know, 16 and up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of people that had to go didn't go because the feeling was that it's not a good feeling.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the men reported, and when I got there, I saw men lined up in the middle of the street in rows of maybe 8 or 10 and down the road.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
